                                    <P class="p47 ft17">BORROWERS REQUEST CUM DECLARATION STATEMENT</P>
                                    <P class="p48 ft18">I, @Model.memberName W/D/o @Model.father hereby confirm that I have undergone the @Model.parameterValue days Compulsory Group Training (CGT) conducted byASIRVAD Microfinance Limited. Where in understood the procedures and systems and accepted all the terms and conditions. I as a loan applicant hereby declare that I interested to avail a loan from ASIRVAD Micro Finance Limited and further declare as under.</P>
                                    <P class="p49 ft0"><SPAN class="ft1">1. </SPAN>My total family income is less than @Model.incomeLimit and as we reside in @Model.areaType area.</P>
                                    <P class="p50 ft0"><SPAN class="ft3">2.</SPAN><SPAN class="ft19">My total level of indebtness is & would be less than 1 Lakh after disbursal of this loan being applied further, I shall neverexceed indebtness of Rs.1.25 Lakh under any circumstances.</SPAN></P>
                                    <P class="p51 ft0"><SPAN class="ft3">3.</SPAN><SPAN class="ft19">I am not a member of any other JLG / SHG and under take that not become member of any other JLG / SHG till the time I have loans running with ASIRVAD Microfinance limited.</SPAN></P>
                                    <P class="p52 ft18"><SPAN class="ft3">4.</SPAN><SPAN class="ft20">I have shared my/family KYC particulars on my own free will and hereby authorize ASIRVADto directly or indirectly carryout credit investigations, CB check back ground checks and other actions including contact my family members, group members, friends, residents of my locality or my referees to establish my credit worthiness, indebtness and default riskpotential risk at any time including prior or after loan sanction / disbursement.`</SPAN></P>
                                    <P class="p53 ft0">a. I understand and agree to pay 1% of loan amount (plus GST) as <NOBR>non-refundable</NOBR> processing fee and (inclusive of GST) and the applicable insurance premium towards Credit Shield Insurance.</P>
                                    <P class="p54 ft0"><SPAN class="ft3">5.</SPAN><SPAN class="ft21">I understand that the effective Annual percentage rate is @Model.interestRate %</SPAN></P>
                                    <P class="p55 ft0"><SPAN class="ft3">6.</SPAN><SPAN class="ft21">I hereby authorize ASIRVAD Microfinance Limited to share my details to agencies approved by regulator/ Government Authorities.</SPAN></P>
                                    <P class="p56 ft0"><SPAN class="ft3">7.</SPAN><SPAN class="ft21">I herewith authorize the insurer to remit the claim amount upon my /spouse death to ASIRVAD Micro Finance limited who will in turn pay to the nominee after adjusting any dues to ASIRVAD.</SPAN></P>
                                    <P class="p57 ft0"><SPAN class="ft3">8.</SPAN><SPAN class="ft21">I hereby authorize ASIRVAD Microfinance Limited to remit the net sanction loan amount after deducting the processing fee+ GST + Applicable insurance premium + Tax into my bank account.</SPAN></P>
                                    <P class="p58 ft18"><SPAN class="ft3">9.</SPAN><SPAN class="ft22">ASIRVAD Microfinance Limited shall be entitled to sell, assign, securitize or transfer its rights and obligations under this loan agreement/promissory note in favour of any bank(s) or financial institution(s) or any other person(s) or agency of ASIRVAD Microfinance Limited's choice in whole or in part of such manner and on such terms and conditions as ASIRVAD Microfinance Limited, may decide and the same shall conclusively be binding upon me.</SPAN></P>
                                    <P class="p59 ft0"><SPAN class="ft3">10.</SPAN><SPAN class="ft23">I understand that a) No Penal charges, no penalty is charged on delayed payment & prepayment.b) No security deposit /margin is being collected for this loan</SPAN></P>
                                    <P class="p60 ft0"><SPAN class="ft3">11.</SPAN><SPAN class="ft24">I Hereby authorize AML to use the mobile number given by me in the application for sending transactional SMS relating to my loan accounts.</SPAN></P>
                                    <P class="p61 ft0">The above contents are filled at my instructions and are read over and explained in the language known to me and my group members by the FDO / Branch / Area Manager and made me understand the details.</P>
                                    <P class="p62 ft18">I, @Model.memberName hereby wilfully declare the information provided herein is true to the bestof my knowledge, information and belief. I have clearly understood the detailed terms & conditions on the loan for which I have hereby applied through this application to ASIRVAD Microfinance Limited. I also confirm to have received the acknowledgement of this loan application. I further understand that this is only a loan application and that ASIRVAD Microfinance Limited has the sole discretion to sanction or reject the loan application or reduce the loan sanction amount.</P>
