                                    <DIV id="id3_2">
                                        @*<P class="p70 ft3">I @Model.memberName W/D/o @Model.father residing at @Model.address (hereafter called as 'Borrower') unconditionally promise to pay (on demand) the payee ASIRVAD Microfinance Limited, at its Head office located at Chennai or at such other place as payee may designate, the loan amount received from ASIRVAD MicrofinanceLimited through NEFT/RTGS/Cheque/Cash of Rs.@Model.loanAmount Rupees (In Words) THIRTY THOUSAND onlywith interest thereon at the rate of @Model.interestRate %</P>
        <P class="p71 ft3"><SPAN class="ft30">p.a. on diminishing balance method from the date hereof through on weekly/fortnightly/ Four weekly/ Monthly to ASIRVAD Microfinance Limited or its authorized employees.</SPAN></P>*@
                                         <P class="p70 ft3">
                                            ON DEMAND, I/WE, @Model.memberName, W/D/o @Model.father (hereafter called as "Borrower" jointly and severally promise to pay to ASIRVAD MICROFINANCE LIMITED (“LENDER”) or order the sum of
                                            Rs. @Model.loanAmount (Rupees @Model.loanAmountTxt Only) together with interest from the date hereof, at @Model.interestRate.% per annum on diminishing balance payable with daily/ fortnightly/4 weekly / monthly/ Quarterly to
                                            Asirvad Microfinance Limited or its authorized employees.
                                        </P>
                                        <div style="border: 1px solid;border-color:black;width: 9%;margin-left: 604px;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;">

